-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- The 'telnetd-ssl' package is now a Recommends as the ftnbbs program is still
the only way to create a user and that is one of the ways it can be accessed.
But need to provide examples of how to use it in the xinetd config file for
the FTNd package, including with the SSL options. (Which can be the default
'snakeoil' cert info for the example, but also means that the ssl-cert pkg
needs to be at least a recommends also?).

